{"tid":344334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓試射洲際導彈　差10分鐘擊中法航客機","createTime":"2017-08-02T08:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T15:31:30.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ca959d061a47393d6eab0c85c2a0e281802d3d6","tid":344334,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T08:15:04.000Z","msg":"北韓上周五晚再成功試射射程可覆蓋整個美國本土的「火星14型」洲際導彈，美國一名官員指，導彈差點擊中一架法航客機。<br />\n<br />\n北韓官方傳媒指，「火星14型」以高角度發射、飛行高度最高3,725公里，47分鐘12秒後落入998公里以外朝鮮半島以東、日本北海道對開的日本專屬經濟區海域。<br />\n<br />\n美國廣播公司報道指，飛行數據顯示，導彈墜入日本海前不足10分鐘，法航293號航班在北海道以西飛過。該架波音777客機由日本東京飛往法國巴黎，載着323人。<br />\n<br />\n法航給美國廣播公司的回應表示，北韓的導彈測試區並不干擾法航客機飛行路徑，該班航機亦沒有遇到任何問題。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部卻對導彈對民航機的潛在威脅表示關注，發言人戴維斯（Jeff Davis）指導彈的確飛過商務客機所使用的繁忙領空。<br />\n<br />\n美國試射導彈前，通常會發新聞稿，但北韓試射導彈卻沒有預先發出警告。"},{"pid":"0771d68d0e8f5055d5ebb018f380dd27a5bc52b0","tid":344334,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T08:15:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170802&amp;guid=57030604&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170802%26guid%3D57030604%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=XxgMDdj0BcTCoetgCbYGd9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=015bbf3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170802%26guid%3D57030604%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=95ae2ef9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170802&amp;guid=57030604&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"564c743d5c7df90578abe03c7bf264e4e46397b7","tid":344334,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"放心啦, 金仔計得好準"},{"pid":"06f6d6417ffc87791811f001eeb6f8d220507c51","tid":344334,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T08:16:08.000Z","m